<td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Strike of Solusek</span><hr size=1> No one in my guild (that I know of) has spell crits off.  Everyone pretty much has melee crits on self only though.  I know when I use my Draughts and crit a lot (it's streaky, in 15 casts I usually crit more than what you suggested) I get comments like &quot;wow you crit a lot!&quot; or &quot;that's a lot of crits.&quot;<br>
